Racing and Container Application
•	Models drivers, cars, and races, as well as container management.
•	Demonstrates composition, object relationships, and OOP design.
•	Main class: DemoApp.java

Requirements
•	Java Development Kit (JDK) 17 or higher
•	IntelliJ IDEA (Community or Ultimate Edition)

Running in IntelliJ IDEA
1.	Open IntelliJ IDEA.
o	Go to File > New > Project from Existing Sources...
o	Select the folder containing these .java files.
2.	Configure JDK.
o	Choose Java SDK 17 or higher.
3.	Mark the source folder.
o	Right-click the folder with .java files → Mark Directory as > Sources Root.
4.	Run the desired application.
o	Open the main file
o	Right-click → Run 'ClassName.main()'.

